des:
The Abu Dhabi National Oil Company or ADNOC is the state-owned oil company of the United Arab Emirates.

Learn more about ADNOC by asking questions about the company.

ADNOC Quiz provides a fun way to test your knowledge about ADNOC.

To start , just say "Alexa, launch Youth development program" or "Alexa, open Youth development program" to start the skill".

At anytime, you can stop the game by saying "Alexa, stop"
